item.title: "Sal DiPeppi (Sebastian Conelli)"
item.description: Good morning! HELLO, everybody! A boom operator with the biggest traps you’ve ever seen, Sal DiPeppi (Sebastian Conelli) is on the show this week! Good morning, GOODbye!

item.title: "Our first Best Of! Howard Stern/Jeff Goldblum/And Many More (Matt Friend)"
item.description: Good Morning, Hellooooooooo! On the show this week, a cavalcade of celebrity visitors! The King of All Media, Howard Stern! A 9-foot-tall goblin man, Jeff Goldblum! America’s Favorite Talker, Andy Cohen! Evil Incarnate, Mitch McConnell! What the- John Oliver! Boo, Donald Trump, boo! A Baboon Man, Paul Giamatti! America’s Favorite Robot-Man, Rami Malek! A Surprise, Timothée Chalamet! and, Funny Man Bill Hader! A fictional man, Tom Wambsgans! The fabulous Tim Gunn!  AND last but not least, Barack Obama! GOOD morning and Goodbye!   (All impressions by Matt Friend, find his work at www.mattfriend.com)

item.description: Good morning, hello! Good morning! Hello! Daisy Maize (Vanessa Bayer), the cutest-shyest paparazzo with the big bow, is on the show this week! Good morning and goodbye!

item.description: Well hello and dare we say good morning! This week we have some hot goss from Dr. Amos Wywanus, a plastic surgeon with loose lips. Good morning goodbye!

item.description: This week we're getting fancy with Debby Schade DePrez Kalb (Patty Guggenheim.) She's the hostess at Maggiano's Little Italy at The Grove. Very classy! Good morning, goodbye!

item.title: "Ron Funches"
item.description: Hello! Good morning! Hello! On the show this week is freakin Ron Funches, as himself. Good morning, goodbye!

item.title: "Corky (Laraine Newman)"
item.description: Good morning hello! This week Jonathan is joined by the one and only Corky- wrangler of all animals Hollyweird. More episodes available exclusively on Stitcher Premium.

item.title: "Brad Pitt (Taran Killam)"
item.description: Good morning hello! After 25 years in the clink, Jonathan is back with his very first podcast episode. To kick things off Jonathan is joined by none other than the Brad Pitt (Taran Killam.) More episodes are available exclusively on Stitcher Premium. Visit stitcherpremium.com/celebrity and use promo code CELEBRITY for FREE listening! Good morning! Good bye!
